node.text:
In Sheep’s Clothing website is a place to find some of the rarest, most beautiful music. It has been a constant source of musical inspiration and escapism for us. It 
also led to the above evening of silliness with this absolute gem. 
Have a listen and enjoy @insheepsclothinghifi

node.text:
Watch my lovely friend @stellamccartney very personal and important film for #breastcancerawarenessmonth 

“A Letter to My Loved Ones is a #NoLessAWoman 2020 film, featuring diverse women bravely baring their souls and scars for #BreastCancerAwareness. Shot during lockdown by Pulitzer Prize-winning photojournalist @LynseyAddario and filmmaker and activist @AliceAedy the group shares their stories while wearing our Louise Listening post-mastectomy bra and #aSMC post-mastectomy sports bra.⁣
⁣
The latest in a long line of campaigns, breast cancer early detection and prevention is a personally important cause to Stella. For 2020, sales of the pink Whitney Popping lingerie set will support our #StellaCares Foundation, aiding breast cancer initiatives globally including @HBCancerUK and the #LindaMcCartneyCentre. A limited number of Louise Listening post-mastectomy bras are also available for free by request at stellamccartneycares.org.⁣
⁣
Discover the #BCA campaign and the women’s letters on #StellasWorld.”
⁣

NoLessAWoman, #StellaCares, #StellaMcCartney, #BCA2020, #BreastCancerAwareness

node.title: A Letter to My Loved Ones by Lynsey Addario

A piece of choreography by Principal of The Royal Ballet @marcisambe created in the memory of George Floyd who was murdered in Minnesota last week.

Nobody should have to live in fear because of the colour of their skin.⁣ #BlackLivesMatter

node.text:
I was asked by @savechildrenuk to join their initiative #savewithstories here’s my reading of “She's Not Good for a Girl, She's Just Good” by @theachopsbooks,  published by @littleboxofbooks, showing kids the world, through amazing stories.
.
Every donation to Save with Stories will help the children and families who’ve been hardest hit by the coronavirus crisis, both in the UK and around the world, providing the most vulnerable families with the food they need, as well as access to early learning resources and simple household goods.
.
If you can, please donate to Save the Children by visiting our website at savethechildren.org.uk/savewithstories. Link in bio.
.
Or you can text STORIES to 70008 to give a one-off donation of £5.
.
Together, we can help families get through this.

ALL MY LOVE!! ❤️

node.text:
Thank you @demellierlondon for my “EARTH TOTE” in honor of #earthday. The word EARTH is subtly debossed on a contrasting leather piece at the front of the bag, evoking the cause it champions and supports protecting the environment by fighting plastic pollution through No More Plastic Foundation.

100% of the profits from the sale of the EARTH tote are donated to No More Plastic @nomoreplasticco 

@demellierlondon also have a permanent charity initiative A Bag, A Life, through which for every item sold DeMellier funds lifesaving vaccines and medical treatments aimed to save the life of a child in need

#sustainablefashion #conciousbrand 🙏🌎😍#notanad
